{"tid":2358821,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"［似曾相識］拜登把衝擊國會大廈的騷亂者稱為國內恐怖分子","createTime":"2021-01-08T11:48:33.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-08T12:09:37.000Z","uid":149494,"like":1,"dislike":4,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"a21d85a5c8369971f2f63ebe794e581922a05566","tid":2358821,"uid":149494,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:48:33.000Z","msg":"候任總統拜登(Joe Biden)把周三衝擊美國國會大廈者稱為國內恐怖分子，談到該暴力事件時，他稱這是「我們國家歷史上最黑暗的日子之一」。<br />\n<br />\n<span class=\"red\">拜登在威爾明頓的講話中稱：「無法把他們稱之為抗議者。」他說道：「他們是一群引發騷亂的暴民。叛亂分子。國內恐怖分子。就是這麼回事。就是這麼明了。」</span><br />\n<br />\n拜登指責總統特朗普(Donald Trump)煽動暴力，稱特朗普已「引發了對美國民主體制的全面攻擊」。白宮暫未回覆置評請求。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://cn.wsj.com/articles/拜登把衝擊國會大廈的騷亂者稱為國內恐怖分子-11610066114?tesla=y\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcn.wsj.com%2Farticles%2F%E6%8B%9C%E7%99%BB%E6%8A%8A%E8%A1%9D%E6%93%8A%E5%9C%8B%E6%9C%83%E5%A4%A7%E5%BB%88%E7%9A%84%E9%A8%B7%E4%BA%82%E8%80%85%E7%A8%B1%E7%82%BA%E5%9C%8B%E5%85%A7%E6%81%90%E6%80%96%E5%88%86%E5%AD%90-11610066114%3Ftesla%3Dy&d=vGGWHGA7%2F8HunCPhnXLTIYleFUCahE4vUWSiCYLfmAs%3D&h=41b7e1af\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://cn.wsj.com/articles/拜登把衝擊國會大廈的騷亂者稱為國內恐怖分子-11610066114?tesla=y</a>"},{"pid":"748d551ca54d3ea5e381de00b44331ca2d85c8e8","tid":2358821,"uid":59976,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:55:30.000Z","msg":"沒有恐襲，只有暴政<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n撤回恐襲定性<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8967f63f5f4046f287ba251c07cd78bf9ec82d6c","tid":2358821,"uid":165361,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T11:56:40.000Z","msg":"BLM 就和平,CLS 世界"},{"pid":"96801815be53c21982a8eede2e120de031d09440","tid":2358821,"uid":262035,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-08T12:09:37.000Z","msg":"左膠雙重標準到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\nblm 燒聯邦建築物就和平<br />\ntrump supporters 衝入國會就terrorist<b